# {{.Name}} ({{.Type}})

Manages a firewall alias on OPNsense. Aliases define groups of hosts, networks, or ports that can be referenced in firewall rules, NAT rules, and other configuration.

Supported alias types include `host`, `network`, `port`, `url`, `urltable`, `geoip`, `networkgroup`, `mac`, `asn`, and others.

